Error: Error: "502 Bad Gateway" When Accessing The Pterodactyl Panel

Solution: 1. Wait and Retry: This error can be a temporary glitch in the server. Wait for a few minutes and try accessing the panel again.

2. Check the Panel URL: Ensure that you have entered the correct URL for your panel. Double-check the URL in your web browser, and make sure you've included "https://" before the domain name.

